HEADWORD: Bilingual
<hw>Bi*lin"gual</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>bilinguis</ets>; <ets>bis</ets> twice + <ets>lingua</ets> tongue,
language.]</ety> <def>Containing, or consisting of, two languages;
expressed in two languages; <as>as, a <ex>bilingual</ex> inscription; a
<ex>bilingual</ex> dictionary</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Bi*lin"gual*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
